Responsibilities
Create design packages including detailed drawings, assembly drawings, and BOM's;
Supporting electrical work proposed baseline changes that arise during the design and work through to completion;
Assist in risk management and risk mitigation strategies;
Maintain design/drawing libraries.
Qualifications
A Bachelor’s Degree in Mechanical Engineering or related field;
A minimum of five years’ mechanical design experience;
Strong familiarity with Solid Edge and AutoCAD;
Experience with engineering change orders (ECOs) and creating engineering documents;
Strong knowledge of problem-solving techniques and facilitation skills;
Excellent oral and written communication skills.
